OL,6,FA teenager has been jailed after he
OL,7,Fkilled two of his friends after
OL,8,Fcrashing into a petrol station in .
OL,10,FOwain Hammett-George, who was 17 at
OL,11,Fthe time, was driving an Alfa Romeo at
OL,12,Fmore than twice the speed limit into
OL,13,Fthe Northway Garage in Bishopston, in
OL,14,FMay 2022.
