OL,6,FHe lost control of the car and hit a
OL,7,Fgrass bank causing the vehicle to flip
OL,8,Finto the air and rotate before
OL,9,Fcolliding with a concrete pillar.
OL,11,FAn investigation into the crash
OL,12,Fdiscovered that Hammett-George was not
OL,13,Fwearing a seatbelt at the time of the
OL,14,Fcollision but had placed the belt into
OL,15,Fits lock and sat on it in order to
OL,16,Fstop the car's warning sound and light
OL,17,Fbeing activated.
