OL,6,FTwo police officers who attended the
OL,7,Fpetrol station after the crash
OL,8,Fdescribed a scene of "utter
OL,9,Fdevastation" with one describing it as
OL,10,F"the worst collision damage they had
OL,11,Fever witnessed in more than two
OL,12,Fdecades".
OL,14,FMr Wright told the court the impact of
OL,15,Fthe crash was so strong that the
OL,16,Fengine of the Alfa Romeo was
OL,17,Fdiscovered 15 metres away from where
OL,18,Fit actually crashed.
