OL,6,FThe prosecution said there was no
OL,7,Fevidence of any pothole and an
OL,8,Finvestigation revealed that at times
OL,9,FHammett-George was driving at more
OL,10,Fthan 70mph, with the car travelling at
OL,11,Fbetween 41mph and 43mph at the time of
OL,12,Fimpact.
OL,14,FAlex Greenwood, mitigating, said
OL,15,FHammett-George had sat in the dock and
OL,16,F"listened intently" to the words of
OL,17,Fthe families of those whose lives he
OL,18,Fhad so deeply affected with his
OL,19,Factions.
