OL,6,FIn a letter written to the court
OL,7,FHammett-George said he is full of the
OL,8,F"deepest and most profound remorse"
OL,9,Fand that he "can't begin to fathom the
OL,10,Fpain it has caused".
OL,12,FHammett-George added: "I was the
OL,13,Fdriver of the vehicle which led to the
OL,14,Funtimely deaths of two precious lives.
OL,15,FI am committed to accepting the legal
OL,16,Fconsequences that will follow as a
OL,17,Fresult. If there was any way I could
OL,18,Fturn back time and prevent this
OL,19,Ftragedy I would do so in a heartbeat."
