OL,6,FAddressing Hammett-George, Judge
OL,7,FGeraint Walters said: "On this
OL,8,Fparticular evening you were in your
OL,9,Fmotor vehicle with three of your young
OL,10,Ffriends. You were showing off.
OL,12,F"You drove at grossly excessive speeds
OL,13,Fto the point where you lost control of
OL,14,Fthe vehicle and immediately
OL,15,Fextinguished the lives of two of those
OL,16,Fin your car, leaving the third
OL,17,Fpassenger with life-changing
OL,18,Fconsequences both physically and
OL,19,Femotionally. "
