OL,6,FJudge Walters added: "I am sadly
OL,7,Fdealing with cases like this
OL,8,Faltogether too frequently. There may
OL,9,Fwell be good reason perhaps for the
OL,10,Fgovernment to consider whether new
OL,11,Fdrivers should be able to carry any
OL,12,Fpassengers. It is not the first time I
OL,13,Fhave said it and it probably won't be
OL,14,Fthe last."
